{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 🔄 Example: Multiplicity Flow in PIRTM\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook illustrates the dynamical evolution of a recursive cognitive tensor \( \\Xi(t) \) under control of the **Universal Multiplicity Constant** \( \\Lambda_m \\).\n",
    "\n",
    "## Goals\n",
    "- Simulate \( \\Xi(t+1) = \\Lambda_m \\Xi(t) T_p + \\Phi(t) \)\n",
    "- Analyze entropy and coherence as functions of \( \\Lambda_m \\)\n",
    "- Visualize tensor flow dynamics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from numpy.linalg import eigvals, norm\n",
    "from sympy import primerange"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 🧱 Prime Tensor Constructor"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def prime_tensor(p, dim=3):\n",
    "    Q, _ = np.linalg.qr(np.random.randn(dim, dim))\n",
    "    return np.log(p) * Q"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 🔁 Evolution Function"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def evolve(Xi, T, Lambda_m=0.85, Phi=None):\n",
    "    if Phi is None:\n",
    "        Phi = np.zeros_like(Xi)\n",
    "    return Lambda_m * Xi @ T + Phi"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 📉 Diagnostics"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def spectral_entropy(eigs):\n",
    "    prob = np.abs(eigs)**2\n",
    "    prob /= np.sum(prob)\n",
    "    return -np.sum(prob * np.log(prob + 1e-9))\n",
    "\n",
    "def phase_coherence(eigs):\n",
    "    return 1 - np.abs(np.sum(np.exp(1j * np.angle(eigs)))) / len(eigs)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## ▶️ Simulation Over Λₘ Values"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "dim = 4\n",
    "T = prime_tensor(11, dim)\n",
    "Lambdas = np.linspace(0.7, 1.1, 25)\n",
    "entropies = []\n",
    "coherences = []\n",
    "\n",
    "for Lambda_m in Lambdas:\n",
    "    Xi = np.eye(dim)\n",
    "    for _ in range(20):\n",
    "        Xi = evolve(Xi, T, Lambda_m)\n",
    "    eigs = eigvals(Xi)\n",
    "    entropies.append(spectral_entropy(eigs))\n",
    "    coherences.append(phase_coherence(eigs))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 📊 Plot: Entropy and Coherence vs. Λₘ"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 4))\n",
    "plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)\n",
    "plt.plot(Lambdas, entropies, label='Entropy')\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Λₘ\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Spectral Entropy\")\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)\n",
    "plt.plot(Lambdas, coherences, label='Coherence', color='green')\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"Λₘ\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"Phase Coherence\")\n",
    "plt.grid(True)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.suptitle(\"Λₘ Flow Control of Ξ(t) Spectrum\")\n",
    "plt.tight_layout()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  }
 ],
